@node "New" "This edition's update overview"

@{b}->  THIS EDITION'S UPDATE OVERVIEW@{ub}

@{b}Newly arrived members:@{ub}
    - BF - Ben Ferrey, starting off with 5 of his records
    - MJ - Michal Janak. Michal sent me records for all of the 16 circuits.
           His E-Mail address isn't in the memberlist yet, because I
           accidentally threw away all the headers of his mail, but I
           do have it somewhere at the Uni :-) And the records are here,
           of course.

    - In the last edition I kind of 'said goodbye' to IV. However, due to
      a case of 'slight' malcommunication, I'm glad to say that he will
      make his return in this edition. He never wanted his records erased,
      but only his entry in the mailing list.
      Sorry about that, Ivanhoe ;) (btw: his times aren't listed as new,
      his delta-score does count from zero) 

    - A thing of which I _am_ sure, is MB's wish to be totally erased.
      Normally other people take care of that (anybody see 'The Net'?
      8), but in this case the 'honour' is mine. Not very much records
      to erase though: none ;) Goodbye, Marcus!

The updates for this edition can be found below. The 1st list shows the
circuits on a 'per member' basis, the 2nd shows the number of updates
'per circuit', and the 3rd one gives the overall count.
The number in parentheses in the 1st list shows where that update ranked.
The average ranking of the member's updates is given last.
@{i}This is the place to monitor your rival's performance!@{ui}

